#: ../../manual/game_engine/physics/types/occluder.rst:27
msgid ""
"Make the \"Occluder\" object take up the whole camera's view with :kbd:`S"
" X 5`. You will see a huge leap in frame rate, since almost nothing is "
"being Rasterized. On my system the Rasterizer step drops to 5ms."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/physics/types/occluder.rst:30
msgid ""
"Try a run with :menuselection:`World properties --> Physics --> Occlusion"
